    {
      "id": "91a0e7f6-589c-4647-ada6-aee541ca51ab",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)}{1+i}$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)}{1+i}\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "dfc50a5e-3910-470e-86e9-0691ffd5b339",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En multipliant numérateur et dénominateur par le conjugué du dénominateur :\n\t\t$$\n\t\t\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)}{1+i}=\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)(1-i)}{(1+i)(1-i)}=\\frac{10+10 i}{2}=5+5 i\n\t\t$$",
        "html": "<p>En multipliant numérateur et dénominateur par le conjugué du\ndénominateur : <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\frac{(1+3\ni)(3+i)}{1+i}=\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)(1-i)}{(1+i)(1-i)}=\\frac{10+10 i}{2}=5+5\ni\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6c380af3-c226-41e7-a844-8e012a96da14",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$(1-i)^8$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\((1-i)^8\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "717ab984-6481-49b0-9ceb-642960c009bd",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On a $(1-i)^2=-2 i$. On en déduit :\n\t\t$$\n\t\t(1-i)^8=\\left((1-i)^2\\right)^4=(-2 i)^4=2^4 \\cdot i^4=16\n\t\t$$",
        "html": "<p>On a <span class=\"math inline\">\\((1-i)^2=-2 i\\)</span>. On en déduit\n: <span class=\"math display\">\\[(1-i)^8=\\left((1-i)^2\\right)^4=(-2\ni)^4=2^4 \\cdot i^4=16\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "94f84a5c-8fd1-4753-b9e4-82e584bc3d21",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\left(\\frac{1+i \\sqrt{3}}{1-i \\sqrt{3}}\\right)^5$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\left(\\frac{1+i \\sqrt{3}}{1-i\n\\sqrt{3}}\\right)^5\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "74f87ab5-2944-404f-9ce6-cde7f1d47e8e",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$$\\begin{align*}\n\t\t\t\\left(\\frac{1+i \\sqrt{3}}{1-i \\sqrt{3}}\\right)^5 & =\\left(\\frac{\\frac{1}{2}+\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}}{\\frac{1}{2}-\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}}\\right)^5 \\\\ &=\\left(\\frac{\\cos \\left(\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)}{\\cos \\left(-\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(-\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)}\\right)^5 \\\\ &=\\left(\\frac{e^{i \\frac{\\pi}{3}}}{e^{-i \\frac{\\pi}{3}}}\\right)^5 \\\\ &=\\left(e^{i \\frac{2 \\pi}{3}}\\right)^5=e^{i \\frac{10 \\pi}{3}} \\\\\n\t\t\t& =e^{-i \\frac{2 \\pi}{3}} \\\\ &=\\cos \\left(-\\frac{2 \\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(-\\frac{2 \\pi}{3}\\right) \\\\\n\t\t\t& =-\\frac{1}{2}-\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}\n\t\t\\end{align*}$$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n            \\left(\\frac{1+i \\sqrt{3}}{1-i \\sqrt{3}}\\right)^5 &amp;\n=\\left(\\frac{\\frac{1}{2}+\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}}{\\frac{1}{2}-\\frac{i\n\\sqrt{3}}{2}}\\right)^5 \\\\ &amp;=\\left(\\frac{\\cos\n\\left(\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)}{\\cos\n\\left(-\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(-\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)}\\right)^5\n\\\\ &amp;=\\left(\\frac{e^{i \\frac{\\pi}{3}}}{e^{-i \\frac{\\pi}{3}}}\\right)^5\n\\\\ &amp;=\\left(e^{i \\frac{2 \\pi}{3}}\\right)^5=e^{i \\frac{10 \\pi}{3}} \\\\\n            &amp; =e^{-i \\frac{2 \\pi}{3}} \\\\ &amp;=\\cos \\left(-\\frac{2\n\\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(-\\frac{2 \\pi}{3}\\right) \\\\\n            &amp; =-\\frac{1}{2}-\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}\n        \\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ff9d4db2-e327-4ff6-a156-70e37256b6ee",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\frac{i}{(1+i \\sqrt{2})^2}$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{i}{(1+i \\sqrt{2})^2}\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "01598459-c7cb-4456-bf7e-16ea796c987e",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$$\\begin{align*}\n\t\t\t\\frac{i}{(1+i \\sqrt{2})^2} & =\\frac{i}{1^2+2 \\sqrt{2} i+(i \\sqrt{2})^2}\\\\ &=\\frac{i}{1-2+2 \\sqrt{2} i}=\\frac{i}{-1+2 \\sqrt{2} i}\\\\ &=\\frac{i(-1-2 \\sqrt{2} i)}{(-1+2 \\sqrt{2} i)(-1-2 \\sqrt{2} i)} \\\\\n\t\t\t& =\\frac{2 \\sqrt{2}-i}{(1+8)} \\\\ &=\\frac{2 \\sqrt{2}}{9}-\\frac{i}{9}\n\t\t\\end{align*}$$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n            \\frac{i}{(1+i \\sqrt{2})^2} &amp; =\\frac{i}{1^2+2 \\sqrt{2}\ni+(i \\sqrt{2})^2}\\\\ &amp;=\\frac{i}{1-2+2 \\sqrt{2} i}=\\frac{i}{-1+2\n\\sqrt{2} i}\\\\ &amp;=\\frac{i(-1-2 \\sqrt{2} i)}{(-1+2 \\sqrt{2} i)(-1-2\n\\sqrt{2} i)} \\\\\n            &amp; =\\frac{2 \\sqrt{2}-i}{(1+8)} \\\\ &amp;=\\frac{2\n\\sqrt{2}}{9}-\\frac{i}{9}\n        \\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
}